This paper focuses on wireless energy transfer in sensor networks, which is a topic related to networked systems and communication (cs.NI). The paper also discusses transmission policies and optimization, which are topics related to information theory (cs.IT) and control systems (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper proposes a new concept and derives an explicit closed-form expression, which are topics related to mathematical analysis (cs.MA). Finally, the paper presents simulation results, which are related to multimedia (cs.MM) as they involve visualizing and analyzing data.
